title: In Colorado, anticipated GOP Senate candidate bows out
text: > Top News In Colorado, anticipated GOP Senate candidate bows out FILE - In this Aug. 7, 2015 file photo, Republican prosecutor George Brauchler speaks with members of the media following the reading of the jury's decision that Colorado theater shooter James Holmes will not receive the death penalty, outside the Arapahoe County District Court in Centennial, Colo. Brauchler, who led the case against the suburban movie theater shooter, has decided not to run for U.S. Senate against Democratic Sen. Michael Bennet.(AP Photo/Brennan Linsley, file)
